			<div class="grid_two block_text_closer">
				<h2 class="h3 ">How to choose the perfect domain for your business or big idea</h2>
				<p class="para_large">Your domain is the foundation of your digital identity. Keep these three tips in mind to make sure you pick a winner.</p>

				<div class="sp3_top_margin"></div>
				<h3 class="para_large">On brand</h3>
				<p>
					If you’re already set on your brand name, your domain should match it. Remember you have many relevant options to choose from, including .APP, .SHOP and hundreds more.
				</p>

				<h3 class="para_large">Concise and clear</h3>
				<p>
					We also own hoverdomains.com, and it’s a fine domain. But hover.com is easier to say, read, and remember.
				</p>
				
				<h3 class="para_large">Easy to type</h3>
				<p>
					Avoid hyphens, numbers, and repeating letters when possible. It makes word-of-mouth referrals easier and decreases the chances someone will mistype your URL.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
